des: WJYK is a radio station of Battaglia Communications, LLC, broadcasting from Chase City, Virginia on 99.3 FM and 980 AM, and streaming worldwide at wjykradio.com and through the WJYK Radio mobile app. The station call letters stand for Worship Jesus Your King. It features Christian music and teaching every day, all day, 24/7.
